# Line-ending normalisation is DISABLED for this repository, deliberately.
#
# CHECKSUMS.sha256 asserts that every frozen artifact here is byte-identical to
# its Zenodo deposit. If Git were allowed to convert line endings on checkout
# (LF -> CRLF on Windows, say), the working-tree bytes would differ from the
# archived bytes and `sha256sum -c CHECKSUMS.sha256` would fail for no reason
# other than platform. For a corpus whose entire value proposition is auditable
# provenance, that would be a self-inflicted wound.
#
# So: no eol conversion, anywhere, on any platform. What was deposited is what
# you get.

* -text

# Belt and braces for the frozen binaries.
*.pdf binary
